rdf:Description.lla:note: Notes in log 2 that Alfred Louis was jailed for 14 days for refusing duty & threatening behaviour. Full note in log2.
Note in log 2 that James Rolles sent to hospital for 5 days in June.
Note in log 2 that James Herbert sent to hospital twice April-June but returned to ship each time.
Notes in log 1 that Hector C Davison was unwilling to carry out his work and displayed drunken and abusive behaviour towards the Master and Mate - see log 1 for full details.
